ðŸ§  How this agent behaves

Purpose:
Itâ€™s the self-verifying, self-publishing GitHub action for your Codexes ecosystem.

Pipeline summary:

1. Checks out the repo and sets up Python.


2. Runs every evolution target (make nexus-aeternum, make finish-evolution, etc.).


3. Validates treasury, ledger, and attestations.


4. Runs symbolic/AI constraint synthesis (XTSG and emoji layers).


5. Builds and deploys docs.


6. Commits any new attestations or final seals.


7. Tags the release with the Omega ID.


8. Publishes the release artifacts (zip, capsule, attestations, treasury, constraints).



